    "en": {
      "title": "Ruhunu Kumari jumps on the tracks",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Railway Department says that the Ruhunu Kumari train which was running from Matara to Maradana has derailed at Bussa area.",
        "Due to this, the train running has been disrupted and the Galle Kumari train running from Beliatte to Maradana has also been stopped at the Galle railway station.",
        "The Department of Railways also says that a special train was run from Aluthgama to Bussa to bring the office workers and other people in the Ruhunu Kumari train who were caught."
      ],
